            <div class="pagetitle__icon">
              <i class="icon-hospital"></i>
            </div>
            <h1 class="pagetitle__heading">Critical Care ICU Facility</h1>
            <p class="pagetitle__desc mb-30">State-of-the-art Intensive Care Unit for critically ill patients requiring advanced monitoring and support.</p>
            <a href="#content" class="scroll-down"><i class="fas fa-long-arrow-alt-down"></i></a>
